  "statusNotes": {
    "type": "doc",
    "version": 1,
    "content": [
      {
        "type": "paragraph",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "text",
            "text": "March 23th: "
          }
        ]
      },
      {
        "type": "bulletList",
        "content": [
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "INFERENG-4707 (llm-d on xKS Cluster Validation): ",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "strong"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "emoji",
                    "attrs": {
                      "shortName": ":green_circle:",
                      "id": "1f7e2",
                      "text": "🟢"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " A validation framework is developed and simplified. Core checks are done, with refining in progress for TCP latency, PCIe topology, and RDMA bandwidth (ETA EOW). "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "high performance",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "em"
                      },
                      {
                        "type": "strong"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " validation is blocked by AKS capacity limits and pending InfiniBand access, particularly hindering RDMA validation which requires multiple nodes.",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "strong"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " Discussion is in progress with microsoft."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "INFERENG-4193 (Must-gather image for llm-d on xKS): ",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "strong"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "emoji",
                    "attrs": {
                      "shortName": ":green_circle:",
                      "id": "1f7e2",
                      "text": "🟢"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " The must-gather tool has been tested on AKS, an OCP bug was fixed, but CKS testing is pending due to permission issues. The plan is to cover AKS, CKS, and OCP baremetal."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "INFERENG-4706 (llm-d on xKS Tech Preview):",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "strong"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "emoji",
                    "attrs": {
                      "shortName": ":green_circle:",
                      "id": "1f7e2",
                      "text": "🟢"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " All tasks are complete except for starting testing, which is blocked by the need for OCP on baremetal access/hardware."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "RHOAIENG-50137 (CI/CD for RHOAI Helm charts):",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "strong"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "emoji",
                    "attrs": {
                      "shortName": ":green_circle:",
                      "id": "1f7e2",
                      "text": "🟢"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " Design is complete to integrate Helm builds into the RHOAI CI flow, including parallel builds, "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "values.yaml",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "code"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " updates, and triggering smoke tests. Next steps involve third-party image approvals and compliance verification."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "listItem",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "paragraph",
                "content": [
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": "RHOAIENG-50184 (RHAI Operator to run llm-d via Kserve on xKS):",
                    "marks": [
                      {
                        "type": "strong"
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " "
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "emoji",
                    "attrs": {
                      "shortName": ":green_circle:",
                      "id": "1f7e2",
                      "text": "🟢"
                    }
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " The code is ready for EA2. Effort is underway to include charts in the operator image for cloud manager in ea2, and a minor testing bug was resolved."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
      }
    ]
  },
